node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.text: @deadstock.app is the first streetwear app to utilize in-house authentication experts plus groundbreaking technology like AI, Blockchain and NFC tags to create a trustworthy, secure and technologically advanced marketplace for sneakerheads and streetwear fanatics. Its in-house authenticators thoroughly inspect every product by hand and assign each verified item with a unique NFC tag, which users can scan with their phone to check the item's Heat Facts, A.K.A. immutable data about that product. With Deadstock, state-of-the-art technology and ultra-secure process eliminate the possibility of imitation or duplication – in other words, canceling out fake products. Head to deadstock.co to learn more. #sponsored

@hypebeaststyle: @kanyewest’s visual style seems to evolve and shift into a new era in line with the release of each of his albums. From the 'College Dropout' years of preppy pink polos to the neo-futurism of 'Graduation,' each release has seen ‘Ye change not only his aesthetic but the visual cues of a generation of fans. With the highly anticipated release of 'DONDA,' we took a quick look at the next phase of 'Ye featuring a darker, broodier, more post-apocalyptic look. Hit the link in bio for the full feature.⁠⁠

@hypebeastwatches: Logic would suggest that the most extravagant watches would be made of the most expensive materials, but there are many examples of steel timepieces commanding the very highest prices in horology. Find out why this is the case via the link in bio.⁠

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: @palaceskateboards and @adidasoriginals have linked up for the former’s Fall collection. Dubbed “PALASTE”, the capsule consists of apparel for wellness activities and leisurewear designed for deep relaxation. The range will drop on August 13 in-stores and online, followed by an arrival in Japan and the Palace WeChat channel on August 14.
Photo: Palace

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: Take a look at the @sacaiofficial x fragment design x @nike LDWaffle navy and grey colorways. Both iterations feature neutral color-blocking and text-based branding with key details such as double stacked Swooshes, “The Classic / Fragment : sacai” written out on the midsoles, and fragment’s bolt logo on one tongue and traditional Nike Sportswear insignias on the other. Early reports have these slated to drop sometime this month but stay tuned for official details.⁠
Photo: @brandon1an

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: @fendi has officially joined forces with @rimowa for a one-of-a-kind suitcase. Coming in two versions, the travel piece is crafted in Rimowa’s signature aluminum casing and features Fendi’s emblematic FF logos as subtle details. Expect both options to arrive in September via Fendi’s stores and website.⁠⁠
Photo: Fendi
